1428
01:14:39,240 --> 01:14:40,276
Chắc chắn rồi.

1429
01:14:44,320 --> 01:14:45,390
MICHAEL: Và...

1430
01:14:46,880 --> 01:14:48,109
Uh... (CLEARS THROAT)

1431
01:14:49,320 --> 01:14:52,836
